5 748 M
(5. 22.2.2.1.1 [lib.facet.num.get.members] get\(...bool&\) omitted) s
5 726 M
(In the list of num_get<> non-virtual members on page 22-23, the) s
5 715 M
(member that parses bool values was omitted from the list of) s
5 704 M
(definitions of non-virtual members, though it is listed in) s
5 693 M
(the class definition and the corresponding virtual is listed) s
5 682 M
(everywhere appropriate.) s
5 660 M
(Proposed Resolution:) s
5 649 M
(Add at the beginning of 22.2.2.1.1 [lib.facet.num.get.members]) s
5 638 M
(another get member for bool&, copied from the entry in 22.2.2.1) s
5 627 M
([lib.locale.num.get].) s
5 594 M
(--------------------------------------------------------------------------) s
5 583 M
(6. 22.2.1.5.2 [lib.locale.codecvt.virtuals] "noconv" definition too vague.) s
5 561 M
(In the definitions of codecvt<>::do_out and do_in, they are specified) s
5 550 M
(to return noconv if "no conversion is needed".  This definition is too) s
5 539 M
(vague, and does not say normatively what is done with the buffers.) s
5 517 M
(Proposed Resolution:) s
5 506 M
(Change the entry for noconv in the table under paragraph 4 in) s
5 495 M
(section 22.2.1.5.2 [lib.locale.codecvt.virtuals] to read:) s
5 473 M
(  noconv: input sequence is identical to converted sequence.) s
5 451 M
(and change the Note in paragraph 2 to normative text as follows:) s
5 429 M
(  If returns _noconv_, the converted sequence is identical to the) s
5 418 M
(  input sequence _[from,from_next\)_._to_next_ is set equal to _to_,) s
5 407 M
(  and the value of _state_ is unchanged.) s
5 374 M
(--------------------------------------------------------------------------) s
5 363 M
(7. 22.2.3.1.2 [lib.facet.numpunct.virtuals] thousands_sep returns wrong type) s
5 341 M
(The synopsis for numpunct<>::do_thousands_sep, and the definition of) s
5 330 M
(numpunct<>::thousands_sep which calls it, specify that it returns a) s
5 319 M
(value of type char_type.  Here it is erroneously described as returning) s
5 308 M
(a "string_type".) s
5 286 M
(Proposed resolution:) s
5 275 M
(In 22.2.3.1.2 [lib.facet.numpunct.virtuals], above paragraph 2,) s
5 264 M
(change "string_type" to "char_type".) s
5 231 M
(--------------------------------------------------------------------------) s
5 220 M
(8. 22.1.1.1.1 [lib.locale.category] codecvt_byname<> instantiations) s
5 198 M
(In the second table in the section, captioned "Required instantiations",) s
5 187 M
(the instantiations for codecvt_byname<> have been omitted.  These) s
5 176 M
(are necessary to allow users to construct a locale by name from) s
5 165 M
(facets.) s
5 143 M
(Proposed resolution:) s
5 132 M
(Add in 22.1.1.1.1 [lib.locale.category] to the table captioned) s
5 121 M
("Required instantiations", in the category "ctype" the lines) s
5 99 M
(  codecvt_byname<char,char,mbstate_t>,) s
5 88 M
(  codecvt_byname<wchar_t,char,mbstate_t>) s
5 55 M
(--------------------------------------------------------------------------) s
