5 781 M
(stream.  A strict reading indicates that it ignores the bits and does) s
5 770 M
(not change them, which confuses users who do not expect eofbit and) s
5 759 M
(failbit to remain set after a successful open.  There are three) s
5 748 M
(reasonable resolutions: 1\) status quo  2\) fail if fail\(\), ignore) s
5 737 M
(eofbit  3\) clear failbit and eofbit on call to open\(\).) s
5 715 M
(Proposed resolution:) s
5 704 M
(In 27.8.1.7 [lib.ifstream.members], _and_ in 27.8.1.10) s
5 693 M
([lib.ofstream.members], under open\(\), one of) s
5 671 M
(  A. no change) s
5 660 M
(  B. Prepend to Effects: "If fail\(\), returns.  Otherwise"...) s
5 649 M
(  C. Prepend to Effects: "Call clear\(\); then," ...) s
5 616 M
